{"tid":2318880,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[客串大聯盟]Charlie Cox「Netflix夜魔俠」將會客串MCU版《蜘蛛俠3》？","createTime":"2020-12-09T16:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T01:17:13.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d7fd7f321031ff1f1ba29f65ddf09a72f06e92a","tid":2318880,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.murphysmultiverse.com/charlie-cox-daredevil-spiderman-3-marvel-studios/?fbclid=IwAR3PQIK2COOY2GGD7PDIgKFdW-1OKNWdcetQLi1xV5u9ojwsNxeN5OJPr9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.murphysmultiverse.com%2Fcharlie-cox-daredevil-spiderman-3-marvel-studios%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3PQIK2COOY2GGD7PDIgKFdW-1OKNWdcetQLi1xV5u9ojwsNxeN5OJPr9A&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=10e73e88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.murphysmultiverse.com/charlie-cox-daredevil-spiderman-3-marvel-studios/?fbclid=IwAR3PQIK2COOY2GGD7PDIgKFdW-1OKNWdcetQLi1xV5u9ojwsNxeN5OJPr9A</a><br />\n<br />\n今年11月29日，Netflix已將Marvel劇集的版權歸還給Marvel Studios自己拍攝，被腰斬的劇集不知未來會如何發展，當中《夜魔俠》劇集去向更受到影迷的關注，因為劇集的故事及班底一直都獲到極高的評價。<br />\n而今日一位知名媒體人Charles Murphy爆料，稱Charlie Cox將會客串MCU版的《蜘蛛俠3》，這次會是《夜魔俠》版權從Netflix回歸Marvel Studios後，首次出現在MCU電影中，更指這個協議其實已經在幾個月前，即版權回歸前談判了，但最終消息當然有待官方宣佈。<br />\n在大約年半之前，已經傳出了他加入的消息，指Peter Parker需要律師援助，而「夜魔俠」Matt Murdock就是不二人選，但當時Charlie Cox迴避了記者的提問，否認了消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#The Avengers-復仇者聯盟(香港粉絲團)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.murphysmultiverse.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dd-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.murphysmultiverse.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2Fdd-1.jpg&h=132581d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4fe9dcab674db58ae109d4c3e3001dfb51fe6cf","tid":2318880,"uid":45766,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T00:32:49.000Z","msg":"2下比人打死喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該時裝出場傾下計算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a661ac9927ce41f1d1c480b717b29d107b0c21","tid":2318880,"uid":249940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:17:13.000Z","msg":"夜魔俠拍season 4好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}